      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "The first of the features today and CESSATION (6) gets the nod. Went to a new level last campaign and looks to be back just as good as she left, judging by her recent trial. She's a speedy customer and she'll carry no weight for Campbell. Can find the front and prove very hard to run down from the front. OSCAR'S FORTUNE (1) comes here without a trial after a strong performance in The Gold Rush. Been a while between drinks but it took a good one to beat him in a similar event when first-up last campaign off a similar set up. Can make an impression. REPOSSESSION (3) showed he was up to this level last campaign and this is a good spot for him. ACROMANTULA (2) makes his first appearance since winning the Miss Andretti Stakes in January. Readied with two trials and is two-time fresh winner.",
